title: O'Neill US Champs
description: Jake Davis winner of the under 16 at the US Champs! The whole event Jake Davis was on point. Winning almost every heat in the under 16 and under 18. He would be at Lowers early every morning to stretch and cram in a surf. Jake would watch precisely before every heat with TM Shaun Ward on his waves selection and line-up placement. With Jake Davis taking the win and Colt Ward taking second team O'Neill had very successful run at this years US Championships!
